HEADWORD: Stopship
<hw>Stop"ship`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A remora. It was fabled to stop ships by attaching itself to
them.</def> <rj><au>Sylvester.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
